Becauſe his two Texts make not only againſt the ſuſpending for a time, but for ever: I wiſh he would preach ſuch Texts as theſe to his people; 

                                 •

                              ▪ Theſ. 5. 12▪ 13. 1▪ Tim. 5. 17. Heb. 13. 7▪ 17.

Which Scripture there applyed, doth hint to any that will not rather cavill then interpret, that my only reaſon for delay of Government was in this: An Angell was yet to come with power and glory; or, the Goſpell would fill the earth with more light; 

                                 •
                              o as we ſhould not ſhut up our ſelves too ſoon in the dark.
